---
title: Baked Chicken & Pesto Risotto with Roasted Pumpkin
description: Enjoy all the flavours of a creamy and rich risotto, without standing over the stove! With tender chicken and sweet roasted pumpkin, this mouth-watering meal will be happily devoured by all.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-chicken-pesto-risotto-92ecf37f.jpg
